{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component."}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Suggestions","type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact"}]},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}]}]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive c